rComments: really helped me feel more comfortable in front of people, lots of fun improvisational challenges. final was really fun, you just have to choreograph your own dance with a group. Sommer is a good dancer, but came off a little uptight and not very approachable. also all the yoga in the class is done wrong, which was a little annoying.

SOMMER ROCKS!!! She pushes you until you have aches and pains, but you always grow in her class. Even if you're not the best dancer, she always challenges her students in an awesome way. Best person to take a class from by far!
She reallly wants you to be creative. As long as you show up and do the activities you will pass, but to do really well she wants you to put yourself out there. Her class was very abstract.
